root header recipient broker
Type: object

Broker

 No Additional Properties

root header recipient broker brokerRegisterNo
Type: string

Register number of the broker. Register number for the independent intermediaries as defined by the IG B2B ; prefix with country code and register plus register number FINMA or FMA (example: CHE-FINMA-F12345678). Note for insurers: For those intermediaries who are not at FINMA or FMA but want to participate on electronic data exchange, e.g., in-house brokers, the code assigned by IG B2B (example: CHE-IGB2B-50001) must be recorded.

 Must match regular expression: ^(CHE\-(FINMA\-F\d{8}|IGB2B\-(\d{5}))|LIE\-FMA\-\d{6})$

Must be at most 19 characters long


Examples:

"CHE-FINMA-F12345678"

"LIE-FMA-12345"

"CHE-IGB2B-12345"

root header recipient broker companyId
Type: string

Unique company identification number (UID) for companies based in Switzerland or EU member states as specified in the UID register of the respective authority.

 Must match regular expression: (CHE|BE|BG|DK|DE|EE|FI|FR|EL|IE|IT|HR|LV|LT|LU|MT|NL|XI|AT|PL|PT|RO|SE|SK|SI|ES|CZ|HU|CY).{2,12}

Must be at most 15 characters long


Example:

"CHE-115.517.011"

root header recipient broker companyName
Type: string

Company name. For a sole proprietorship, name and surname must be entered.

Must be at most 255 characters long


Example:

"MyCompany Name"

root header recipient broker brokerBranch
Type: string

IGB2B Number of the branch, agency of the broker, broker entitled to commission. Can be HQ or deviation branch. Mandatory if the broker is the sender of the event

 Must match regular expression: ^\d{6}$

Must be at most 6 characters long


Examples:

"101156"

"320000"

root header recipient insurer companyName

Company name. For a sole proprietorship, name and surname must be entered.

root header recipient insurer insurerCode
Type: string

Unique company code for insurer, according to list IG B2B

 Must match regular expression: ^[a-zA-Z0-9]+$

Must be at most 5 characters long

"15S"

Type: string

Must be at most 7 characters long

Type: object

Main NOGA-Code. Required in offer request. One of UVGRiskNo and NOGACodeMain must be provided in offer.
